#: trndi.api.nightscout.sparamdesc
msgid ""
"NightScout v2 setup (use FULL access token):\n"
"\n"
"1) Open your NightScout site (e.g., https://your-site).\n"
"2) Go to Admin -> Tokens — or API Secret.\n"
"3) If you use Tokens:\n"
"   - Create a token with at least READ scope.\n"
"   - Copy the FULL access token value exactly as shown.\n"
"4) In Trndi:\n"
"   - Address: enter your NightScout URL\n"
"   - Auth: paste the FULL access token (not just a suffix).\n"
"\n"
"Note: If you instead use the legacy API Secret, paste your API Secret value as-is."
msgstr ""

#: trndi.api.nightscout.sparamdeschtml
msgid "<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;\"><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">🌙 NightScout v2 Setup</h2><p style=\"color: #7f8c8d; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 15px;\">(use FULL access token)</p><ol style=\"padding-left: 20px;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Open your NightScout site (e.g., <code style=\"background: #6495ED; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">https://your-site</code>).</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Go to <strong>Admin → Tokens</strong> — or <strong>API Secret</strong>.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">If you use Tokens:<ul style=\"margin-top: 5px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li>Create a token with at least <strong>READ</strong> scope.</li><li>Copy the <strong>FULL</strong> access token value exactly as shown.</li></ul></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">In Trndi:<ul style=\"margin-top: 5px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li><strong>Address:</strong> enter your NightScout URL</li><li><strong>Auth:</strong> paste the FULL access token (not just a suffix).</li></ul></li></ol><p style=\"border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 10px; margin-top: 15px;\"><strong>⚠️ Note:</strong> If you instead use the legacy API Secret, paste your API Secret value as-is.</p></div>"
msgstr "<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;\"><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">🌙 NightScout v2-Einrichtung</h2><p style=\"color: #7f8c8d; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 15px;\">(vollständiges Access-Token verwenden)</p><ol style=\"padding-left: 20px;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Öffnen Sie Ihre NightScout-Seite (z.B. <code style=\"background: #6495ED; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">https://ihre-seite</code>).</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Gehen Sie zu <strong>Admin → Tokens</strong> — oder <strong>API Secret</strong>.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Falls Sie Tokens verwenden:<ul style=\"margin-top: 5px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li>Erstellen Sie ein Token mit mindestens <strong>READ</strong>-Berechtigung.</li><li>Kopieren Sie den <strong>vollständigen</strong> Access-Token-Wert genau wie angezeigt.</li></ul></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">In Trndi:<ul style=\"margin-top: 5px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li><strong>Adresse:</strong> Ihre NightScout-URL eingeben</li><li><strong>Auth:</strong> das VOLLSTÄNDIGE Access-Token einfügen (nicht nur ein Suffix).</li></ul></li></ol><p style=\"border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 10px; margin-top: 15px;\"><strong>⚠️ Hinweis:</strong> Falls Sie stattdessen das ältere API Secret verwenden, fügen Sie Ihren API-Secret-Wert unverändert ein.</p></div>"

#: trndi.api.nightscout.sparampassword
msgctxt "trndi.api.nightscout.sparampassword"
msgid "API Secret"
msgstr "API-Geheimnis"

#: trndi.api.nightscout.sparamusername
msgctxt "trndi.api.nightscout.sparamusername"
msgid "NightScout URL"
msgstr "NightScout-URL"

#: trndi.api.nightscout3.sparamdesc
msgid ""
"** ALPHA DRIVER - Please use \"NightScout\" for daily use! **\n"
"NightScout v3 setup (use FULL access token):\n"
"\n"
"1) Open your NightScout site (e.g., https://your-site).\n"
"2) Go to Admin -> Tokens — or API Secret.\n"
"3) If you use Tokens:\n"
"   - Create a token with at least READ scope.\n"
"   - Copy the FULL access token value exactly as shown.\n"
"4) In Trndi:\n"
"   - Address: enter your NightScout URL\n"
"   - Auth: paste the FULL access token.\n"
"\n"
"Tip: Both \"abc123\" and \"token=abc123\" formats are accepted.\n"
"Note: If you instead use the legacy API Secret, paste your API Secret value as-is.\n"
"Note 2: Your access token should look like: trndi-abc123 (or whatever name you chose)"
msgstr ""

#: trndi.api.nightscout3.sparamdeschtml
msgid "<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;\"><div style=\"background: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; border: 2px solid #c82333;\">⚠️ ALPHA DRIVER - Please use \"NightScout\" for daily use! ⚠️</div><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">🌙 NightScout v3 Setup</h2><p style=\"color: #7f8c8d; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 15px;\">(use FULL access token)</p><ol style=\"padding-left: 20px;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Open your NightScout site (e.g., <code style=\"background: #6495ED; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">https://your-site</code>).</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Go to <strong>Admin → Tokens</strong> — or <strong>API Secret</strong>.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">If you use Tokens:<ul style=\"margin-top: 5px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li>Create a token with at least <strong>READ</strong> scope.</li><li>Copy the <strong>FULL</strong> access token value exactly as shown.</li></ul></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">In Trndi:<ul style=\"margin-top: 5px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li><strong>Address:</strong> enter your NightScout URL</li><li><strong>Auth:</strong> paste the FULL access token.</li></ul></li></ol><div style=\"border-left: 4px solid #0d6efd; padding: 12px; margin-top: 15px; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0;\"><strong>💡 Tip:</strong> Both <code style=\"background: #6F8FAF; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">abc123</code> and <code style=\"background: #6F8FAF; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">token=abc123</code> are accepted.</p></div><div style=\"border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 12px; margin-top: 15px; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0;\"><strong>📝 Note:</strong> If you instead use the legacy API Secret, paste your API Secret value as-is.</p><p style=\"margin: 0;\"><strong>📝 Note 2:</strong> Your access token should look like: <code style=\"background: #6F8FAF; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">trndi-abc123</code> (or whatever name you chose).</p></div></div>"
msgstr "<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6;\"><div style=\"background: #dc3545; color: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; border: 2px solid #c82333;\">⚠️ ALPHA-TREIBER - Bitte \"NightScout\" für den täglichen Gebrauch verwenden! ⚠️</div><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">🌙 NightScout v3-Einrichtung</h2><p style=\"color: #7f8c8d; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 15px;\">(vollständiges Access-Token verwenden)</p><ol style=\"padding-left: 20px;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Öffnen Sie Ihre NightScout-Seite (z.B. <code style=\"background: #6495ED; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">https://ihre-seite</code>).</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Gehen Sie zu <strong>Admin → Tokens</strong> — oder <strong>API Secret</strong>.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">Falls Sie Tokens verwenden:<ul style=\"margin-top: 5px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li>Erstellen Sie ein Token mit mindestens <strong>READ</strong>-Berechtigung.</li><li>Kopieren Sie den <strong>vollständigen</strong> Access-Token-Wert genau wie angezeigt.</li></ul></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">In Trndi:<ul style=\"margin-top: 5px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li><strong>Adresse:</strong> Ihre NightScout-URL eingeben</li><li><strong>Auth:</strong> das VOLLSTÄNDIGE Access-Token einfügen.</li></ul></li></ol><div style=\"border-left: 4px solid #0d6efd; padding: 12px; margin-top: 15px; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0;\"><strong>💡 Tipp:</strong> Sowohl <code style=\"background: #6F8FAF; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">abc123</code> als auch <code style=\"background: #6F8FAF; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">token=abc123</code> werden akzeptiert.</p></div><div style=\"border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 12px; margin-top: 15px; border-radius: 4px;\"><p style=\"margin: 0 0 8px 0;\"><strong>📝 Hinweis:</strong> Falls Sie stattdessen das ältere API Secret verwenden, fügen Sie Ihren API-Secret-Wert unverändert ein.</p><p style=\"margin: 0;\"><strong>📝 Hinweis 2:</strong> Ihr Access-Token sollte so aussehen: <code style=\"background: #6F8FAF; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px;\">trndi-abc123</code> (oder welchen Namen Sie gewählt haben).</p></div></div>"

